snippet.title: Side-effects of Note Ban: Bank Employees Working Hard after Demonetisation of Rs 500, 1000

localized.description:
Side-effects of Demonetisation: Bank Employees are working hard to solve cash crunch after ban on currency notes of Rs 500 and Rs 1000. A woman employee got heart attack during work.
